OL,1,D]S737{kkkc5FBritish Army 'tried to     
OL,2,D]S555{jjj25Frecruit IRA man's widow'   
OL,3,D]Suuu{rrzq5F                           
OL,4,T#######################################
OL,5, The widow of a man murdered by the IRA 
OL,6, as an informer, has told the BBC that  
OL,7, the British Army tried to recruit her  
OL,8, as an informant.                       
OL,10,FClaire Dignam said she was shocked by  
OL,11,Fthe approach, which was made following 
OL,12,Fthe death of her husband, John, in     
OL,13,F1992.                                  
OL,15,FIt is believed he was killed because he
OL,16,Fwas suspected of working for the       
OL,17,FBritish security services.             
OL,19,FThe Ministry of Defence said it could  
OL,20,Fneither confirm nor deny the claims.   
